<div
class='bg-img'
id='home'
style='background-image:url("img/bg/bg2.jpg")'>
  <div class='bg-center-container'>
    <h1 class='bg-heading'>
      About Shirin Shamsi
    </h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class='grid-x grid-padding-x grid-container grid-padding-y add-padd'  data-equalizer>
  <div class='shrink large-offset-1 cell out-vc'  data-equalizer-watch>
    <div class='in-vc'>
      <img src='img/profile-pic/aditi.png'>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='medium-6 large-6 cell out-vc'  data-equalizer-watch>
    <div class='in-vc'>
      <p class='web-pro-text'>
        To be a writer of children’s books has been my dream for many years. It quite takes my breath away when I imagine myself daring to join the realms of those esteemed heroes, whose words have nourished my soul? I am compelled to write. Writing ignites my soul and makes me feel alive.
        The Girl Who Dared, an Early Reader published by Teacher Created Materials
      </p>
      <a class="hollow button" href="./Aditi-Gurkar">Learn More About Shirin Shamsi </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div
class='bg-img'
id='research'
style='background-image:url("img/bg/bg3.jpg")'>
  <div class='bg-center-container'>
    <h1 class='bg-heading'>
      Books
    </h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class='grid-x medium-up-3 grid-padding-x grid-container grid-padding-y add-padd'  data-equalizer>
  <% for (let i = 0; i < results.books.length; i++) { %>
    <div class='cell'>
      <div class='my-card'>
        <div 
          class='card-img'
          style='background-image: url("<%=results.books[i].image %>");'
        ></div>
        <h4><%=results.books[i].title %></h4>
        <p>
          <%=results.books[i].description %>
        </p>
        <a class="hollow button" href="<%=results.books[i].link %>">Get This Book</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% } %>
</div>

